{"tid":742756,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致我最愛的你","createTime":"2018-07-14T22:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T23:42:24.000Z","uid":161495,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bff04e0593d1dec5ac6528bf27b8d37fd0b592a8","tid":742756,"uid":161495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T22:25:01.000Z","msg":"曾經,<br />\n兩顆孤獨的心緊緊相依。<br />\n<br />\n如今,<br />\n兩個獨立的人各走各路。<br />\n<br />\n曾經,<br />\n我以為你我之間並無他。<br />\n<br />\n如今,<br />\n我卻無可避免變成了他。<br />\n<br />\n你的憂鬱和我的孤僻,<br />\n<br />\n這亦令我們互相吸引。<br />\n<br />\n你的溫柔和我的風趣,<br />\n<br />\n曾令我以為天作之合。<br />\n<br />\n你的服從和我的任性,<br />\n<br />\n令我以為會長相廝守。<br />\n<br />\n曾經,<br />\n你我在摩天輪許下諾言。<br />\n<br />\n如今,<br />\n你和他在家中床上纏綿。<br />\n<br />\n曾經,<br />\n你是我夢中的唯一繆斯。<br />\n<br />\n如今,<br />\n我知道我的夢卻是如此。"},{"pid":"ff2ec7b894ecede496b7d4f98d1cf293e3809064","tid":742756,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T23:42:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://xanga.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fxanga.com&d=qbdn2e%2BZltgxhYmaxHhzdWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=f540d5a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">xanga.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ig.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fig.com&d=qbdn2e%2BZltgxhYmaxHhzdWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=41c9b0ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ig.com</a><br />\n #diary"}]}